    <briefdescription>
<para>Per-device I2C circuit breaker. Mix into any class that talks to an I2C device. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Usage: <computeroutput>class Foo : public <ref refid="classOpenSkyhawk_1_1OutputBase" kindref="compound">OutputBase</ref>, public <ref refid="classOpenSkyhawk_1_1I2cHealth" kindref="compound">I2cHealth</ref> { bool <ref refid="classOpenSkyhawk_1_1I2cHealth_1a43673387ef8d4452cebc52e425c7e00b" kindref="member">i2cProbe()</ref> override {...} };</computeroutput> then <computeroutput>if (!i2cReachable()) return;</computeroutput> before any I2C transaction. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
